## Prerequisites

* Bash 3.2+
* vcprompt - https://github.com/ericmeyer/vcprompt
* rvm
* git
* hg

## Use

* clone project into your home dir.  (The project assumes it resides in $HOME/.bash)
* mkdir $HOME/.bash/machine_specific
* add the following line to the end of your bash_login/bashrc file:
  . $HOME/.bash/source_all
* custom stuff should go in files in the $HOME/.bash/machine_specific/ dir or in the original bash_login/bashrc file

## Notes

* set your PATH environment variable!  (It is untouched by default.)